Var<T> - Class in plugins.adufour.vars.lang
Vars is a library built on the concept of Java boxed types, but with the following enhancements: Boxed values can be changed (not possible with Java boxed primitives) Pseudo-"Pass-by-Reference" mechanism: a variable may reference another variable A listener mechanism to respond to "valued-changed" or "reference-changed" events A GUI library providing ready-to-use graphical components linked to each variable A VarEditorModel interface allowing to simplify the GUI generation The Var class is the top-level class of all variables.
